name: MongOCOM
body:
### Welcome to MongOCOM Project Page.
Mongo Object-Collection Mapper (MongOCOM) is an Object-oriented document mapper for [mongoDB](mongodb.org). If you want to help us, feel free to clone our repository:

```
$ git clone git@github.com:javaboybr/MongOCOM.git

```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
